Elio Motors
Elio Motors is an American vehicle manufacturer committed to revolutionizing how consumers think about transportation. The company's enclosed, three-wheeled vehicle, the Elio, is a low-cost, highly fuel-efficient vehicle with a targeted $7,450* base price and is projected to get up to 84 MPG. The vehicle will be engineered to the industry's highest safety standards and built at a former General Motors plant in Shreveport, Louisiana. 




