Company Overview


Elio Motors, Inc. is a designer, developer and manufacturer of highly efficient, low cost three-wheeled vehicles. Leveraging existing automotive technologies and partnerships with the world's leading automotive engineering firms and component suppliers, Elio Motors is engineering and building a high quality, safe, environmentally-friendly vehicle - the Elio - for sale initially in the United States market. 




