Tour Events


Elio live. The tour.
As you might expect from a true automotive rock star, Elio does its most exciting work on tour, center stage. And like any true fan, you want to score front row. You want to
                        get up close and personal. You want to ooh and ahh side by side with the press and tech gurus. And you definitely want to see it in action on the road. But enough
                        preaching to the choir. Here’s the schedule:
                    
Note: Dates, Times and Locations are subject to change without notice, and new ones may be added. Please check back frequently




